<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>161</hymn_number>
<author>Peter Perkins Pitchlynn, Watts</author>
<title>&quot;The everlasting Song&quot; ƲIT161</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Yakni 'lʋppak ash biekʋt</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yakni 'lʋppak ash biekʋt
 Sa chu̱kʋsh atukma
 Ai isht alotoho̱wa na,
 Ant a himakʋshke.

[V2]
 Himak a pilla hokʋno,
 A̱ki holitopa
 A binili pulla kak o̱
 Pit pihi̱sa lashke.

[V3]
 Yʋmmak o̱ Chihowa yokʋt
 A tohwikeli na,
 Sai Okchalinchi Klaist okʋt
 A mi̱kot binili.

[V4]
 Ʋba hatak moyuma kʋt
 A yukpa chinto hosh
 Afoluplit a hielit
 A taloho̱wʋshke.
 5 Chisʋs pi̱ holitopa ma!
 Pi ai okcha̱ya ma!
 Ahanchit, isht taloho̱wʋt,
 Yukpa, hosh aiasha.

[V5]
 Ona lish, ʋno ak kia
 Enchel a̱ toba lish,
 Iba yukpa li hokbano,
 Aiahni li hoke.

[V6]
 Yʋmmak ahe, aiahni hosh
 Himak ak inli ho̱,
 Ʋbanumpa holitopa
 Ai a̱hlit sa yimmi.

[V7]
 Ʋba A̱ki Chihowa ma!
 Is si apela na,
 Yʋmmak oka chim ona lish,
 Taloho̱wa lashke.

[V8]
 Chisʋs pulla anukchetot,
 Ilʋppa puta kʋt
 Ʋm a̱hla hi oka, ahnit
 Il im issa lishke.</lyrics>
</song>